The french government formally abolish rule suspend September set limit import sale refine oil product outside European Community. The rule introduce 1979 require importer buy 80 pct refine product European refiner 90 pct refine product sell France require French European refiners. The abolition rule together relaxation administrative procedure publish official journal today. French oil industry official immediately criticise move encourage import french refiner make heavy losses. Industry figure publish February show industrywide loss billion franc take account extraordinary loss stock depreciation. Reuter 